{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9427c64395","title":"鸣放言论及大字報","origin":"《西南师范学院资產阶级反动右派言论汇集》第二辑，中共西南师范学院委员会宣传部西南师范学院马列主义教研组编，1958年3月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2dec157524","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":4,"articleId":"9427c64395"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"6aca127908","name":"王益善"},{"id":"b86e073e34","name":"西南师范学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bd8250bb87","type":"title","text":"鸣放言论及大字报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"d49c82ceef","type":"authors","text":"西南师范学院王益善","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"87a52b4ea0","type":"subtitle","text":"（王益善：西南师范学院历史系1957级学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"c2b68f4afa","type":"subtitle","text":"（一）王益善在班会上的发言（摘要）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"39701edd87","type":"paragraph","text":"六月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"ea6410aaad","type":"paragraph","text":"我们班上第一二学年虚假繁荣，三学年是破裂时期，四学年是危机时期。班上是封建统治，直到现在很多人不敢说话。班上是一团糟，不民主。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"26ffeb563c","type":"paragraph","text":"六月五日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"cc91ab00fb","type":"paragraph","text":"……我国各方面都是由党一手包办……是否只有共产党员才能领导呢？中央到地方组织都应有各民主党派参加，由有能力的民主党派人士参加领导。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"7e8d81fe4a","type":"paragraph","text":"党委制是宗派主义、官僚主义产生的温床，同时使许多党员仗此势力来专断，在学校产生严重的矛盾，这制度起了很大作用。人事处的神秘化就是由于没有民主党派人士参加。……大多数的系主任有职无权。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"4dc80e4c3d","type":"paragraph","text":"在分配问题上，服从祖国分配，变成了服从党员分配。在教育系，党小组将全班排队成上中下，最后对同学进行判决。……我们提出的民主办校还未通过实践，应在实践中来看究竟谁更好。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"2a663989a6","type":"paragraph","text":"关于“走内线”的问题[注一]我完全同意高国正的看法。我班确实有“走内线”的人，而且有的成功了。党员应检查自己是否是走内线入党的。未入党的同志也应检查。这问题是全院普遍存在的问题。应问党发展党员的方针是什么？希望党委能重视、解决此问题，因这关系着党员是否能起作用的问题。班上的党员有百分之八十我是不承认的。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"e0d0927c07","type":"paragraph","text":"六月六日","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"1549c496a1","type":"paragraph","text":"过去思想改造属于思想战线上的阶级斗争，同时是带有人民内部性质的问题。知识分子的思想是小资产阶级思想，这部分改造属于人民内部问题。在思想改造中各级领导者在掌握中央方针时，常以简单、粗暴方式，用的是阶级斗争的办法，犯了许多错误，搞错了许多人。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"c67b2238fa","type":"paragraph","text":"六月×日","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"ebb9492109","type":"paragraph","text":"党之用人唯党。政府机关最高负责人有一党包办情况，总理中没有民主人士参加，不符合毛主席提出的联合政府形式。……主张撤消党支部书记在系三头中的职权，只参加系委会。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"0cf8965680","type":"paragraph","text":"党员只喜欢跟他接近和唱一个调的“积极分子”……所以，造成有些人“走内线”，拉私人关系入党。……不说话，不发表内心反对意见，一味奉上级旨意执行，这是党所认为的“老实”。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"5b45ca7009","type":"paragraph","text":"马列主义教研室是清一色，排挤出邓托夫、李景白老师。[注二]","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"061baf4889","type":"paragraph","text":"党员享受在前，吃苦在后。……毕代汉的遭遇是我班宗派主义体系造成的[注三]。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"74c8767c7c","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反斗争中的积极分子是另有企图的，运动中错误不少。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"fc796de9d8","type":"paragraph","text":"张院长高高在上，把学校变成了机关，不学习业务。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"bd6e0365b1","type":"paragraph","text":"班上党员未起作用，无群众基础，自高自大看不起人，只教育别人不说真话，有思想问题只在党内谈，会上唱高调。入党后就高人一等，产生了特权思想。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"9c527999d4","type":"paragraph","text":"党员干部乱汇报，整人，为自己寻找政治资本——升官发财，党群关系因之恶化。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"d2c5c9b24f","type":"paragraph","text":"学习苏联是硬搬，如五年一贯制不好，五级分制不合用，马列主义基础课不结合中国大学的情况，成了“教条”。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"0744e6c040","type":"paragraph","text":"分配工作时，所谓教育是大帽子压人。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"885c307c45","type":"paragraph","text":"文教政策方面，教育发展冒进，学生来源差，志愿不能照顾，中学生教中学，……课程标准过高过大，“万金油”过多，如马列主义学校卫生及革命史等。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"3ec2965ae1","type":"paragraph","text":"怀疑共产党代表绝对真理。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"ff32184561","type":"paragraph","text":"人民日报社论〈这是为什么？〉起了坏的作用。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"f15a5fe59c","type":"paragraph","text":"[注一]高国正，史四学生，“走内线”是右派分子们用以打击靠拢党的积极分子的“武器”，此词与所谓“阿谀逢迎”“拍马屁”等为同义词。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"e629402e82","type":"paragraph","text":"[注二]“清一色”之说不符合事实，马列主义教研室迄今仍有不少非党员教师，邓、李调他系是由于全院教学的需要。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"0c01458bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"[注三]“毕代汉”，史四学生，右派分子，思想反动，把组织教育说成是对他的陷害。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"16cf78e7fa","type":"subtitle","text":"（二）会上与会后（大字报）     白帆[发表本文时所用的笔名]","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"40a4b33045","type":"paragraph","text":"按：这是王益善意在丑化历史系一位党负责同志的打油诗。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"4a43a3544e","type":"paragraph","text":"会上她特别和蔼可亲，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"dddb35c708","type":"paragraph","text":"征询意见是那么真诚：","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"f45fff9df3","type":"paragraph","text":"“我热忱表示欢迎","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"3b4d63117e","type":"paragraph","text":"希君畅所欲言，言无不尽”","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"7d322dd62f","type":"paragraph","text":"会后，她杏眼圆睁，目光逼人，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"151ae0bbc1","type":"paragraph","text":"声音你（？）何来狮吼。春雷震鸣：","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"173e80bd10","type":"paragraph","text":"“哼！简直是打击别人！","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"e242ce606d","type":"paragraph","text":"我知他们是别有用心？”","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"08d9e31fb2","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"73a6d834f4","type":"paragraph","text":"原来她听惯了吹捧，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"bab20f387a","type":"paragraph","text":"昏昏然飘飘然直上青云，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"a10f3f03af","type":"paragraph","text":"这下揭开了疮巴——三大主义，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"a336cdfe2b","type":"paragraph","text":"惊醒了人家美梦，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"0d9e890fc4","type":"paragraph","text":"咋不叫她怒气填膺。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"56f4b759c4","type":"paragraph","text":" （一九五七年六月十日）","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"1aa4cc2640","type":"subtitle","text":"（三）微词（大字报）      白帆[发表本文时所用的笔名]","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"9b4cc1e892","type":"paragraph","text":"嗳呀！我的支部书记，","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"57e417df8d","type":"paragraph","text":"爱唱歌，跳舞","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"b1d89884f6","type":"paragraph","text":"你说是轻佻，放荡。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"38603bf096","type":"paragraph","text":"爱看小说，杂志，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"93b1c2f9ec","type":"paragraph","text":"你批评是“不务正业”？","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"a0899bd443","type":"paragraph","text":"爱向领导提意见，","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"b7e86a58ef","type":"paragraph","text":"你斥责是“目无组织”！","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"efa50b51b2","type":"paragraph","text":"不说不笑，","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"b85de355f7","type":"paragraph","text":"又说是思想有问题。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"67e80fc701","type":"paragraph","text":"嗳呀！我的首长——支部书记","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"0873045beb","type":"paragraph","text":"你叫我咋个办呢？","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"9cee405ccf","type":"paragraph","text":"我看你神经有些恍惚，需要喝点“镇静剂”。","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"2cc1324c51","type":"paragraph","text":" （一九五七年六月十日）","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"ebc32feebc","type":"subtitle","text":"（四）揭开粪坑盖（大字报）     庶人[发表本文时所用的笔名]","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"f4de8f5ff7","type":"paragraph","text":"史四党干部","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"c95a6dc6c6","type":"paragraph","text":"绰绰有“功勋”","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"585bc215ae","type":"paragraph","text":"统治连四戴","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"f657d1c3f4","type":"paragraph","text":"黎民含冤深","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"ee16712657","type":"paragraph","text":"有话不敢讲","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"d05b87f350","type":"paragraph","text":"有冤无处申","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"52199638f1","type":"paragraph","text":"敢有鸣不平","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"cae33e92fa","type":"paragraph","text":"被认为奸人","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"ad0c026c2a","type":"paragraph","text":"“反党，反革命”","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"17b0e99378","type":"paragraph","text":"含血来喷人","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"90a5811da0","type":"paragraph","text":"逼人把颈吊","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"b39026757a","type":"paragraph","text":"逼人发神经","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"545e3698ed","type":"paragraph","text":"怨声载满道","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"90605552d9","type":"paragraph","text":"班上死沉沉","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"33c0585858","type":"paragraph","text":"他却献媚相","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"3d4aa69fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"投机报喜讯","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"298d82d25f","type":"paragraph","text":"“要作先进班”","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"3fb57d3360","type":"paragraph","text":"要当优秀生","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"50b03263a3","type":"paragraph","text":"借此来入党","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"e7159f6f87","type":"paragraph","text":"仗势欺良民","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"386002fc9a","type":"paragraph","text":"帽子满天飞","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"4d3570ab6a","type":"paragraph","text":"表面装正经","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"012eb64d16","type":"paragraph","text":"里头臭气熏","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"3d8e3d5a6d","type":"paragraph","text":"不学又无术","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"37fa1f416b","type":"paragraph","text":"先后恋爱经","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"c173ae2233","type":"paragraph","text":"只图吃党饭","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"20246a9f89","type":"paragraph","text":"借此把官升","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"e0d8e55df4","type":"paragraph","text":"劝你快改正","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"8f90471c40","type":"paragraph","text":"赵高是前人！","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"},{"id":"3293c7f5a2","type":"paragraph","text":" （一九五七年六月十日）","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395"}],"page":{"id":"1b4a5a816b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9427c64395","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}